    {"id":12,"type":"mc","score":4,"question":"$2 \\leq x \\leq 5$이면 $-x + 3$의 범위는?","choices":["$-2 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 1$","$1 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 5$","$-2 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 0$","$-1 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 2$","$0 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x$가 최대 $5$이면 $-x+3$은 최소 $-2$. $x$가 최소 $2$이면 $-x+3$은 최대 $1$. 따라서 $-2 \\leq -x+3 \\leq 1$"},
    {"id":13,"type":"mc","score":4,"question":"$2(x - a) < x + 3$의 해가 $x < 5$일 때 $a$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$-1$","$2$","$-2$","$3$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x < 3+2a$. 해가 $x<5 \\Rightarrow 3+2a=5 \\Rightarrow a=1$"},
